==方式==
===手術===
[[輸精管切除術|輸精管切除術]]（男性結紮）是利用手術方式切除部份[[輸精管|輸精管]]，達到[[絕育|無法生育]]的目的，手術中會將二條輸精管各切除一部份，並且將開口處電燒或是縫合，使[[精子|精子]]無法進入[[精液|精液]]中。輸精管切除術可以在醫院或是診所進行。美國疾病控制與預防中心（CDC）研究估計在每一千人結紮後，二年內失效（讓配偶或性伴侶懷孕）的人數會有11人，其中有過半是出現在輸精管切除術後的頭三個月，在72週後就沒有失效的情形了。在輸精管切除術後，輸精管內仍有殘留的精子，一般要在手術三個月後精液內才會沒有精子<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.plannedparenthood.org/health-topics/birth-control-4211.htm |title=Birth Control Methods - Birth Control Options |publisher=Plannedparenthood.org |date= |accessdate=2017-03-17 |archive-date=2014-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140317091759/http://www.plannedparenthood.org/health-topics/birth-control-4211.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，一般也會建議進行精液檢查確認精子數量已降到零。

===保險套===
[[保險套|保險套]]是長條型薄膜的屏障式避孕用具，在性交時使用，可以減少[[懷孕|懷孕]]的可能性，也可以減少[[性傳播疾病|性傳播疾病]]（例如[[HIV|HIV]]）的風險。保險套的用法是在陰莖勃起時套入陰莖上，當男性射精時，精液（及其中的精子）會保留在保險套內，不會進入性伴侶的體內<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/condom |title=Condom | Definition of Condom by Merriam-Webster |publisher=Merriam-webster.com |date= |accessdate=2016-05-14 |archive-date=2009-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090424232222/http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/condom |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
在理想情形下，使用保險套避孕的失效率為每年2%<ref name="hatcher">{{cite web|url=http://www.contraceptivetechnology.com/table.html|title=Contraceptive Technology (19th ed.).|author1=Hatcher, RA|author2=Trussel,J|author3=Nelson,AL|author4=|year=2007|accessdate=2016-10-10|display-authors=etal|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080531095926/http://www.contraceptivetechnology.com/table.html|archivedate=2008-05-31}}</ref><ref name="simultaneous">{{cite journal |author1=Kestelman, P |author2=Trussell, J |title=Efficacy of the simultaneous use of condoms and spermicides | journal = Fam Plann Perspect | volume = 23 | issue = 5 |pages=226–7, 232 |year=1991| pmid = 1743276 | doi = 10.2307/2135759 |jstor=2135759}}</ref>。

保險套可以配合其他的避孕方式（例如[[殺精劑|殺精劑]]）一起使用，會有更好的避孕效果<ref name="simultaneous"/>。一般使用保險套避孕時的懷孕機率因人而異，大約每年比率從10%到18%不等<ref name="Kippley1996">{{cite book | first=John | last=Kippley |author2=Sheila Kippley | year=1996 | title=The Art of Natural Family Planning | url=https://archive.org/details/artofnaturalfami0000kipp | edition=4th addition | publisher=The Couple to Couple League | location=Cincinnati, OH | page=[https://archive.org/details/artofnaturalfami0000kipp/page/146 146] | isbn=0-926412-13-2}}, which cites:
:{{cite journal |last=Guttmacher Institute |title=Choice of Contraceptives | journal = The Medical Letter on Drugs and Therapeutics | volume = 34 |pages=111–114 |year=1992|pmid=1448019 |issue=885 }}</ref>。

===性交中斷法===
[[性交中斷法|性交中斷法]]是在進行陰道性行為時，在射精前將陰莖移出性伴侶的陰道，若每次都正確的使用，一年內的失敗率為4%。一般若使用性交中斷法避孕，每年的失敗率為22%<ref name="cont tech 18">{{cite book | first=RA | last=Hatcher | year=2000 | title=Contraceptive Technology | edition=18th | publisher=Ardent Media | location=New York | isbn=0-9664902-6-6 | url=http://www.contraceptivetechnology.org/table.html | name-list-format=vanc | author2=Trussel J | author3=Stewart F | display-authors=2 | access-date=2017-03-17 | archive-date=2013-09-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130901110131/http://contraceptivetechnology.org/table.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
==歷史==
約公元40年，古希臘藥理學家[[迪奥科里斯|迪奥科里斯]]在《[[藥物論|藥物論]]》中提出用[[大麻種子|大麻種子]]及[[芸香|芸香]]（Ruta graveolens）作避孕，《藥物論》也是中古時期廣為使用的文獻<ref>{{cite book|url=http://www.therenaissanceman.org/images/DIOSCORIDES-Books_2_-_4.doc|title=De Materia Medica|author=Dioscorides|year=ca. 40 A.D.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110728100517/http://www.therenaissanceman.org/images/DIOSCORIDES-Books_2_-_4.doc|archivedate=2011-07-28}} (translated by Goodyer (1655), modified and published 1933 by Robert Gunther).  The herbs are said to "extinguish conception".</ref>。有一個用大鼠進行的實驗（使用由80%乙醇溶液萃取的萃取物20mg），發現可以讓精子量減少到一半以下<ref>{{cite journal |author=Sailani MR, Moeini H |title=Effect of Ruta graveolens and Cannabis sativa alcoholic extract on spermatogenesis in the adult wistar male rats |journal=Indian Journal of Urology |volume=23 |issue=3 |pages=257–60 |date=2007-07 |pmid=19718326 |pmc=2721602 |doi=10.4103/0970-1591.33720|last2=Moeini }}</ref>。在中古時期的波斯（及其他傳統文化）曾用這類草藥作為男性避孕用，其他也用作男性避孕的包括[[锦葵科|锦葵科]]的[[草棉|草棉]]<ref>{{cite journal|vauthors=Hadley MA, Lin YC, Dym M |title=Effects of gossypol on the reproductive system of male rats|journal=J. Androl. |year=1981|issue=2|pages=190–9}}</ref>、[[莎草科|莎草科]]的高莎草（''Cyperus longus''）、[[马鞭草科|马鞭草科]]的''Vitex pseudonegundo''、[[藜亚科|藜亚科]]的[[土荆芥|土荆芥]]（''Chenopodium ambrosioides''）<ref>{{cite journal |author=Khaleghi Ghadiri M, Gorji A |title=Natural remedies for impotence in medieval Persia |journal=International Journal of Impotence Research |volume=16 |issue=1 |pages=80–3 |date=2004-02 |pmid=14963476 |doi=10.1038/sj.ijir.3901153|last2=Gorji }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/S0378-8741(79)80014-8 |author=Conway GA, Slocumb JC |title=Plants used as abortifacients and emmenagogues by Spanish New Mexicans |journal=Journal of Ethnopharmacology |volume=1 |issue=3 |pages=241–61 |date=1979-10 |pmid=232204|last2=Slocumb }}</ref>、[[馬兜鈴科|馬兜鈴科]]的{{le|馬兜鈴秈稻|Aristolochia indica}}（''Aristolochia indica''）<ref>{{cite journal |author=Pakrashi A, Pakrasi PL |title=Antispermatogenic effect of the extract of Aristolochia indica Linn on male mice |journal=Indian Journal of Experimental Biology |volume=15 |issue=4 |pages=256–9 |date=1977-04 |pmid=914334|last2=Pakrasi }}</ref>、[[石榴屬|石榴屬]]的[[石榴|石榴]]<ref>{{cite journal |author=Prakash AO |title=Anti-implantation activity of some indigenous plants in rats |journal=Acta Europaea Fertilitatis |volume=16 |issue=6 |pages=441–8 |year=1985 |pmid=3832714 |name-list-format=vanc|author2=Saxena V |author3=Shukla S |display-authors=3 |last4=Tewari |first4=RK |last5=Mathur |first5=S |last6=Gupta |first6=A |last7=Sharma |first7=S |last8=Mathur |first8=R}}</ref>及[[蘿摩科|蘿摩科]]的''Sarcostemma acidum''<ref>{{cite journal |author=Venma PK |title=Effect of Sarcostemma acidum stem extract on spermatogenesis in male albino rats |journal=Asian Journal of Andrology |volume=4 |issue=1 |pages=43–7 |date=2002-03 |pmid=11907627 |name-list-format=vanc|author2=Sharma A |author3=Mathur A |display-authors=3 |last4=Sharma |first4=P |last5=Gupta |first5=RS |last6=Joshi |first6=SC |last7=Dixit |first7=VP}}</ref><!--- Reference list stolen from Sailani et al. table above --->。不過由草棉萃取出來的化學物質，以及其他由{{le|棉籽|Cottonseed}}及[[秋葵|秋葵]]籽萃取出的化學物質（[[棉酚|棉酚]]）已被禁用作避孕用途，因為有10%至20%的使用者出現永久性的不孕<ref>{{cite journal |author=Coutinho EM |title=Gossypol: a contraceptive for men |journal=Contraception |volume=65 |issue=4 |pages=259–63 |date=2002-04 |pmid=12020773 |doi=10.1016/S0010-7824(02)00294-9}}</ref>。

在傳統印度醫學[[阿育吠陀|阿育吠陀]]中，[[蘇胥如塔|蘇胥如塔]]及書籍《Rasarathasamucchaya》、《{{le|Sarangadhara|Sarangadhara}}》、《Bhavaprakasha》及《Bhisagya Ratnavali》都曾提過用[[楝樹|楝樹]]來避孕。此草藥傳統上就是用在避孕的用途上，楝樹葉實驗後可以降低雄性大鼠造成其他雌鼠受孕的比例，即使受孕，產子數也下降<!--and litter size--><ref>{{cite journal |author=Deshpande VY, Mendulkar KN, Sadre NL |title=Male antifertility activity of Azadirachta Indica in mice |journal=Journal of Postgraduate Medicine |volume=26 |issue=3 |pages=167–70 |date=1980-07 |pmid=7205685 |url=http://www.jpgmonline.com/article.asp?issn=0022-3859;year=1980;volume=26;issue=3;spage=167;epage=70;aulast=Deshpande |last2=Mendulkar |last3=Sadre |access-date=2017-03-18 |archive-date=2017-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318173938/http://www.jpgmonline.com/article.asp?issn=0022-3859;year=1980;volume=26;issue=3;spage=167;epage=70;aulast=Deshpande |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1995年時研究者發現[[中藥|中藥]][[雷公藤|雷公藤]]中分離出有避孕效果的化學物質<ref>{{cite journal |author=Zhen QS, Ye X, Wei ZJ |title=Recent progress in research on Tripterygium: a male antifertility plant |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_contraception_1995-02_51_2/page/121 |journal=Contraception |volume=51 |issue=2 |pages=121–9 |date=1995-02 |pmid=7750290 |doi=10.1016/0010-7824(94)00018-R|last2=Ye |last3=Wei }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chsa.org.cn/html/xkpx/xjy/2015/1125/218.html|title=男性节育方法研究的进展|author=唐文豪|date=2015-11-25|access-date=2017-03-18|publisher=中國性學會|quote=雷公藤（Tripterigium wilfordii hook）。雷公藤是我国科研人员继棉酚之后,于1983年发现的另一种抗生育药。雷公藤以前主要用于治疗自體免疫性疾病和过敏性疾病，对生殖系统的作用仅被认为是其毒副作用之一。|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170227203257/http://chsa.org.cn/html/xkpx/xjy/2015/1125/218.html|archive-date=2017-02-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2002年時有研究者將[[番木瓜|番木瓜]]籽中的萃取物餵食猴子，在餵食90天後，其射精的精液中已沒有精子<ref>{{cite journal |author=Lohiya NK |title=Chloroform extract of Carica papaya seeds induces long-term reversible azoospermia in langur monkey |journal=Asian J. Androl. |volume=4 |issue=1 |pages=17–26 |date=2002-03 |pmid=11907624 |name-list-format=vanc|author2=Manivannan B |author3=Mishra PK |display-authors=3 |last4=Pathak |first4=N |last5=Sriram |first5=S |last6=Bhande |first6=SS |last7=Panneerdoss |first7=S }}</ref>。番木瓜籽傳統即用來避孕，而在針對大鼠進行的長期實驗中，對睪丸或是其他器官也沒有顯著的不良影響<ref>{{Cite journal| doi = 10.1016/j.jep.2009.11.007| pmid = 19914367| year = 2010| last1 = Goyal | first1 = S.| last2 = Manivannan | first2 = B.| last3 = Ansari | first3 = A.| last4 = Jain | first4 = S.| last5 = Lohiya | first5 = N.| title = Safety evaluation of long term oral treatment of methanol sub-fraction of the seeds of Carica papaya as a male contraceptive in albino rats.| volume = 127| issue = 2| pages = 286–291| journal = Journal of Ethnopharmacology }}</ref>。

{{le|熱基避孕|Heat-based contraception}}早在[[希波克拉底|希波克拉底]]時代就已提出，是提高睪丸的溫度以避免生成精子。此一避孕法需要讓睪丸在攝氏47度（恰好低於疼痛閾值）下維持45分鐘，此一技術較不受歡迎，但另一個衍生技術是應用[[超聲波|超聲波]]達到類似目的，已經在進行先期評估<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newmalecontraception.org/new-methods-3/ultrasound/|title=Heat Methods of Male Contraception|publisher=Male Conception Information Project|accessdate=2017-03-18|archive-date=2013-04-15|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130415112830/http://www.newmalecontraception.org/new-methods-3/ultrasound/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==相關研究==
男性避孕的目標是找出可逆的男性避孕方式，可能是透過藥物、手術或是其他方式。

===藥物===
有關男性避孕藥的研究，有許多相關的研究和二種給藥方式有關：一個是類似女性[[复合口服避孕药|复合口服避孕药]]的男性口服激素避孕藥<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2012/08/120816121950.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-03-20 |archive-date=2018-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180310200708/https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2012/08/120816121950.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，另外一種是男性避孕激素注射<ref>{{cite journal | pmid = 15105800 | doi=10.1016/j.ajog.2004.01.057 | volume=190 | issue=4 Suppl | title=Male hormonal contraception | date=2004-04 | journal=Am. J. Obstet. Gynecol. | pages=S60–8| author1=Wang | first1=C | last2=Swerdloff | first2=R. S. }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=吳培 |title=我們仍然沒有男士避孕良方，但這並非因為男人是懦夫 |url=https://theinitium.com/article/20170417-dailynews-male-contraceptive/ |work=端傳媒 |publisher=端傳媒 |date=2017-04-17 |accessdate=2017-04-18 |archive-date=2017-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170419101742/https://theinitium.com/article/20170417-dailynews-male-contraceptive/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

* [[棉酚|棉酚]]（Gossypol）是棉花的萃取物，科學家曾探討是否可以作為口服避孕丸使用，棉酚可以減少精子的數量，不過有20%的機率會讓精子數量永遠減少，即使不再使用棉酚也無法回到可生育的狀態<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Coutinho|first1=EM|title=Gossypol: a contraceptive for men.|journal=Contraception|date=2002-04|volume=65|issue=4|pages=259–63|pmid=12020773|doi=10.1016/s0010-7824(02)00294-9}}</ref>
*有一種避孕方式是透過和{{le|BRDT|BRDT}}蛋白質（Bromodomain testis-specific protein）上特定區域結合，來抑制{{le|染色体重建|chromatin remodeling}}，此作法已確認可以在公小鼠身上有避孕效果，而且是可逆的<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2012-08/dci-amc081412.php |title=A male contraceptive pill in the making? |deadurl=no |accessdate=2012-08-17 |archive-date=2016-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610185355/http://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2012-08/dci-amc081412.php }}</ref>。 科學家正在研發{{le|JQ1|JQ1}}，是以上述方式作用的選擇性BRDT抑制劑，屬於非激素類的男性避孕藥。可以有效的讓睪丸不生產精子，也沒有之前研究的激素類男性避孕藥會出現的[[不良反应_(医学)|不良反应]]<ref name="pmid22901802">{{cite journal |vauthors=Matzuk MM, McKeown MR, Filippakopoulos P | title = Small-Molecule Inhibition of BRDT for Male Contraception | journal = Cell | volume = 150 | issue = 4 | pages = 673–684 |date=2012-08 | pmid = 22901802 | pmc = 3420011 | doi = 10.1016/j.cell.2012.06.045 | url = |display-authors=etal}}</ref>。
*針對精子[[抗原|抗原]]的{{le|免疫避孕法|Immunocontraception}}，已確認對於雄性的靈長類有效<ref>{{cite journal|last=O'Rand|first=MG|author2=EE Widgren |author3=P Sivashanmugam |author4=RT Richardson |author5=SH Hall |author6=FS French |author7=CA Vande Voort |author8=SG Ramachandra |author9=V Ramesh |author10=A Jagannadha Roa |title=Reversible immunocontraception in male monkeys immunized with Eppin|journal=Science|year=2004|volume=306|pages=1189–90|doi=10.1126/science.1099743|pmid=15539605|issue=5699|bibcode=2004Sci...306.1189O}}</ref>。
*像[[硝苯地平|硝苯地平]]等類的[[钙离子通道阻滞剂|钙离子通道阻滞剂]]可以改變精子的脂質代謝方式，使精子無法和卵子受精，也就達到避孕的目的<ref>{{cite journal |author=Hershlag A, Cooper GW, Benoff S |title=Pregnancy following discontinuation of a calcium channel blocker in the male partner |journal=Human Reproduction |volume=10 |issue=3 |pages=599–606 |date=1995-03 |pmid=7782439 |url=http://humrep.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=7782439|last2=Cooper |last3=Benoff }}</ref>。從2010年6月起在以色列[[巴伊兰大学|巴伊兰大学]]的研究，發現一次給藥可以有五年的效果。在小鼠身上進行的測試有避孕效果，而且沒有副作用<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://msmagazine.com/blog/blog/2010/07/02/a-pill-for-men-still-five-years-away/ |title=A Pill for Men–Still Five Years Away |accessdate=2017-03-20 |archive-date=2012-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120916052555/http://msmagazine.com/blog/blog/2010/07/02/a-pill-for-men-still-five-years-away/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 有一種影響[[維生素A|維生素A]]代謝途徑的化合物已證實可以讓公的小鼠沒有精子，且不影響其[[性衝動|性衝動]]。只要停止服藥，小鼠就會繼續產生精子。正常情形下，維生素A會轉換成活性成份[[視黃酸|視黃酸]]，之後和視黃酸受體結合，以啟動精子的產生，但此化合物讓維生素A無法轉換為視黃酸，也就不會產生精子<ref name=livescience>Parry, Wynne [http://www.livescience.com/14440-male-birth-control-pill-sperm-vitamin.html?_r=1&hp "New Male Birth Control Concept Shows Promise"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.livescience.com/14440-male-birth-control-pill-sperm-vitamin.html?_r=1&hp |date=20170320232735 }}, ''LiveScience, 2011-06-04, accessed 2011-06-06.</ref><ref>{{cite journal | pmid = 21505053 | year = 2011 | last1 = Chung | first1 = SS | last2 = Wang | first2 = X | last3 = Roberts | first3 = SS | last4 = Griffey | first4 = SM | last5 = Reczek | first5 = PR | last6 = Wolgemuth | first6 = DJ | title = Oral Administration of a Retinoic Acid Receptor Antagonist Reversibly Inhibits Spermatogenesis in Mice | volume = 152 | issue = 6 | pages = 2492–2502 | doi = 10.1210/en.2010-0941 | pmc = 3100616 | journal = Endocrinology}}</ref>。有許多方式可以達到上述目的，例如阻斷稱為RALDH3（ALDH1A2），在睪丸中將[[視黃醛|視黃醛]]轉換為視黃酸的{{le|醛脫氫酶|aldehyde dehydrogenase}}。不過以往類似的試驗失敗了，因為阻斷用的化合物專一性不足，也阻斷了其他醛類的脫氫作用，例如在乙醇代謝中需要的一些脫氫作用，造成了嚴重的副作用<ref name=Science2012>{{cite journal|journal=Science|author=Sam Kean|title=Reinventing the Pill: Male Birth Control|year=2012|volume=338|pages=318–320|doi=10.1126/science.338.6105.318|pmid=23087225|issue=6105}}</ref>。另一個方式是直接阻斷視黃酸受體，不過也會有嚴重的副作用<ref name=livescience/>。
*{{le|Adjudin|Adjudin}}是一種類似{{le|氯尼达明|lonidamine}}但沒有毒的物質，已確認可以讓小鼠有可逆性的避孕效果<ref>{{cite journal |author=Mruk DD, Cheng CY |title=Sertoli-Sertoli and Sertoli-germ cell interactions and their significance in germ cell movement in the seminiferous epithelium during spermatogenesis |journal=Endocrine Reviews |volume=25 |issue=5 |pages=747–806 |date=2004-10 |pmid=15466940 |doi=10.1210/er.2003-0022|last2=Cheng }}</ref>。此藥物破壞睪丸中[[塞爾托利氏細胞|塞爾托利氏細胞]]之間的連結，也影響其形成[[精細胞|精細胞]]的能力。因此精子在尚未成熟時就釋放出來，無法成為有受精功用的[[配子|配子]]。有一種新的靶向遞送機制使得Adjudin有更好的效果<ref>{{cite journal |author=Mruk DD, Wong CH, Silvestrini B, Cheng CY |title=A male contraceptive targeting germ cell adhesion |journal=Nature Medicine |volume=12 |issue=11 |pages=1323–8 |date=2006-11 |pmid=17072312 |doi=10.1038/nm1420|last2=Wong |last3=Silvestrini |last4=Cheng }}</ref>。
*{{le|Gamendazole|Gamendazole}}是氯尼达明的衍生物，在大鼠身上有半可逆的避孕效果。一般認為其作用機制也是破壞塞爾托利氏細胞的功能，因此造成[[激活素与抑制素|抑制素B]]的減少<ref name=Tash>{{cite journal|last=Tash|first=Joseph|title=A Novel Potent Indazole Carboxylic Acid Derivative Blocks Spermatogenesis and Is Contraceptive in Rats after a Single Oral Dose|journal=Biology of Reproduction|date=2008-07|volume=78|issue=6|pages=1127–1138|doi=10.1095/biolreprod.106.057810|pmid=18218612|last2=Attardi|first2=B|last3=Hild|first3=SA|last4=Chakrasali|first4=R|last5=Jakkaraj|first5=SR|last6=Georg|first6=GI}}</ref>。
* 目前已發展了許多男性的荷爾蒙避孕劑。其中有一種是混合型，包括注射[[Depo-Provera|Depo-Provera]]以避免[[精子发生|精子发生]]，配合典型的[[睪酮_(藥物)|睾酮]]凝膠以補充荷爾蒙<!--<ref name="Finn">{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/S0029-7437(07)70395-6 |first1=Robert |last1=Finn |date=2007-05 |title=Male Contraceptive Methods Are in the Pipeline |journal=Ob. Gyn. News |volume=42 |issue=9 |pages=8 |url=http://www.obgynnews.com/article/S0029-7437%2807%2970395-6/preview |doi-broken-date=2017-01-15 }}{{Dead link|date=2019年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>--><ref>Nuzzo R (2006) [http://www.latimes.com/features/health/la-he-lab16oct16,0,4285327,full.story Beyond condoms: male hormonal contraceptives may finally be on track] {{Wayback|url=http://www.latimes.com/features/health/la-he-lab16oct16,0,4285327,full.story |date=20200430084018 }}. ''Los Angeles Times'', 2006-10-16.</ref>。另一個作法包括每年植入的皮下植入物，會分泌合成的睾酮化合物（7α-methyl-19-nortestosterone），再配合定期的Depo-Provera注射<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.popcouncil.org/research/ment-subdermal-implants-for-men|title=MENT®: Subdermal Implants for Men -  Population Council|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-13|archive-date=2017-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171230103528/http://www.popcouncil.org/research/ment-subdermal-implants-for-men|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在第二期臨床實驗中，若只有皮下植入物（沒有注射Depo-Provera）但是給最高劑量，大部份的實驗結果都已經出現[[无精症|精子數量明顯不足]]的情形<ref name="Eckardstein 2003">{{cite journal |author=Sigrid von Eckardstein |title=A clinical trial of 7α-methyl-19-nortestosterone implants for possible use as a long-acting contraceptive for men |journal=The Journal of Clinical Endocrinology and Metabolism |volume=88 |issue=11 |pages=5232–9 |date=2003-11 |pmid= 14602755|doi=10.1210/jc.2002-022043 |author2=Gabriela Noe |author3=Vivian Brache |display-authors=3 |last4=Nieschlag |first4=Eberhard |last5=Croxatto |first5=Horacio B. |last6=Alvarez-Sanchez |first6=Francisco |last7=Moo-Young |first7=Alfred J. |last8=Sivin |first8=Irving |last9=Kumar |first9=Narender |last10=Small |first10=Margaret |last11=Sundaram |first11=Kalyan}}</ref>。另外一個作法是每月注射{{le|睾酮十一酸酯|testosterone undecanoate}}，在中國的第三期臨床實驗中結果很好<ref name="Gu 2003">{{cite journal |author=Gu YQ |title=A multicenter contraceptive efficacy study of injectable testosterone undecanoate in healthy Chinese men |journal=The Journal of Clinical Endocrinology and Metabolism |volume=88 |issue=2 |pages=562–8 |date=2003-02 |pmid=12574181 |doi=10.1210/jc.2002-020447 |name-list-format=vanc|author2=Wang XH |author3=Xu D |display-authors=3 |last4=Peng |first4=L |last5=Cheng |first5=LF |last6=Huang |first6=MK |last7=Huang |first7=ZJ |last8=Zhang |first8=GY}}</ref><ref name="Gu 2009">{{cite journal |author=Gu Y |title=Multicenter contraceptive efficacy trial of injectable testosterone undecanoate in Chinese men |journal=The Journal of Clinical Endocrinology and Metabolism |volume=94 |issue=6 |pages=1910–5 |date=2009-06 |pmid=19293262 |doi=10.1210/jc.2008-1846 |name-list-format=vanc|author2=Liang X |author3=Wu W |display-authors=3 |last4=Liu |first4=M. |last5=Song |first5=S. |last6=Cheng |first6=L. |last7=Bo |first7=L. |last8=Xiong |first8=C. |last9=Wang |first9=X.}}</ref>。
* {{le|苯氧基苯甲胺|Phenoxybenzamine}}有抑制射精的效果，因此也有潛力成為有效的避孕藥。研究發現在停藥後，精液就有生育效果，因此避孕的結果是可逆的<ref>{{cite journal |author=Kjaergaard N, Kjaergaard B, Lauritsen JG |title=Prazosin, an adrenergic blocking agent inadequate as male contraceptive pill |journal=Contraception |volume=37 |issue=6 |pages=621–9 |date=1988-06 |pmid=2899490 |doi=10.1016/0010-7824(88)90008-X|last2=Kjaergaard |last3=Lauritsen }}</ref>。
* {{le|Trestolone|Trestolone}}是一種合成代謝的的類固醇，可以顯著的減少精子數量<ref>{{cite web|title=MENT®: Subdermal Implants for Men {{!}}  Population Council|url=http://www.popcouncil.org/research/ment-subdermal-implants-for-men|website=www.popcouncil.org|accessdate=2017-01-23|archive-date=2017-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171230103528/http://www.popcouncil.org/research/ment-subdermal-implants-for-men|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 手術 ===
* {{le|RISUG|RISUG}}英文全名是Reversible inhibition of sperm under guidance，手術方式是將溶於[[二甲基亞碸|二甲基亞碸]]內的{{le|苯乙烯馬來酸酐|styrene maleic anhydride}}聚合物凝膠注射到輸精管中。聚合物本身有正電荷，當帶有負電荷的精子經過時，電位差會破壞精子<ref name="bare_url">[http://blog.advocatesaz.org/2011/08/08/expanding-options-for-male-contraception/] {{Wayback|url=http://blog.advocatesaz.org/2011/08/08/expanding-options-for-male-contraception/ |date=20120427184237 }} Expanding Options for Male Contraception. Planned Parenthood Advocates of Arizona. 2011-08-08. Retrieved 2012-04-01.</ref>。若要恢復生育能力，可以再進行一次注射，會洗去聚合物凝膠，即可恢復生育能力。{{As of|2011}}，已在印度進行針對病患的[[臨床試驗#Ⅲ期临床试验|Ⅲ期临床试验]]，在美國、印度、中國及孟加拉都已申請專利。{{le|Vasalgel|Vasalgel}}是一個聚合物凝膠注射的廠牌名稱，正在美國進行試驗，已經完成兔子的試驗，初期試驗的結果都良好，因此預計在2015年進行人類的臨床試驗<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newmalecontraception.org/vasalgel/|title=Male Contraception Information Project » Vasalgel|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-13|archive-date=2014-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140920161934/http://www.newmalecontraception.org/vasalgel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* {{le|輸精管阻塞法|Vas-occlusive contraception}}包括一些讓二條[[輸精管|輸精管]]部份阻塞或是完全阻塞的手術，和[[输精管切除术|输精管切除术]]切除部份输精管的作法不同，但目的都是使精子無法通過。輸精管內裝置（intra vas device，IVD）及其他注射栓塞是暫時性的阻塞输精管，若進行手術將阻塞物取出，即可恢復生育能力。[[美国食品药品监督管理局|美国食品药品监督管理局]]（FDA）已核可2006年輸精管內裝置的人體臨床試驗<ref>{{cite journal |title=Male Contraceptive Methods Are in the Pipeline |first=Robert |last=Finn |journal=Ob. Gyn. News |volume=42 |issue=9 |pages=28 |date=2007-05-01 |url=http://imn.gcnpublishing.com/fileadmin/content_pdf/obn/archive_pdf/vol42iss9/70395_main.pdf }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

=== 其他===
* 也有避孕是用[[超音波|超音波]]殺死精子來進行的，概念來自1970年代Mostafa S. Fahim發現超音波會殺死[[微生物|微生物]]，且會降低精子受孕能力，其用在人類避孕的安全性及有效性仍在研究中<ref name=Murray>{{cite web|last=Murray|first=Rheana|title=Ultrasound kills sperm, could be the future of male birth control: study|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/breaking-news/ci_19843262|publisher=Daily News|accessdate=2012-01-30|date=2012-01-30|archive-date=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108112903/http://www.mercurynews.com/breaking-news/ci_19843262|dead-url=no}}</ref>。到2012年為止，有針對大鼠進行的實驗，大鼠在溫鹽浴中進行二次各15分鐘的超音波處理，二次處理之間隔了二天，結果將其精子量降到可受孕的水平之下<ref name="Tsuruta"/><ref name=Murray/>。另一個小型研究是和狗有關，在進行三次超音波後，狗射精時精液中已沒有精子<ref name="bare_url" />。有許多進一步的研究，包括對人是否有效、效果可持續的程度，以及其安全性，都還要再進行探討<ref name=Murray/>。

===已中止的研究===
* {{le|Miglustat|Miglustat}}（Zavesca 或 NB-DNJ）是核可治療多種罕見的脂质储存障碍疾病的藥物。在小鼠實驗中，可以提供有效及完全可逆的避孕效果，但這個效果只針對實驗室中有特殊基因的小鼠有效，在其他的動物身上沒有避孕效果<ref>{{cite journal |author=Amory JK |title=Miglustat has no apparent effect on spermatogenesis in normal men |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_human-reproduction_2007-03_22_3/page/702 |journal=Human Reproduction |volume=22 |issue=3 |pages=702–7 |date=2007-03 |pmid=17067996 |doi=10.1093/humrep/del414 |name-list-format=vanc|author2=Muller CH |author3=Page ST |display-authors=3 |last4=Leifke |first4=E. |last5=Pagel |first5=E.R. |last6=Bhandari |first6=A. |last7=Subramanyam |first7=B. |last8=Bone |first8=W. |last9=Radlmaier |first9=A.}}</ref>。
* {{le|西洛多辛|Silodosin}}（Silodosin）是高度尿道選擇性（uroselectivity）的α1肾上腺素受体拮抗剂，FDA核可用來治療[[良性前列腺增生|良性前列腺增生]]（BPH），發現若使用到正常劑量的五倍，可以減少精子數量<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ema.europa.eu/docs/en_GB/document_library/EPAR_-_Public_assessment_report/human/001209/WC500074188.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-03-20 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050256/http://www.ema.europa.eu/docs/en_GB/document_library/EPAR_-_Public_assessment_report/human/001209/WC500074188.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

